Blocks.Text: each bidder has a value distribution Di
seller observes {Di}i and computes a price p
bidders arrive one by one, each bidder observes own value Vi~Di and decides
to accept or reject price p
if accept: seller gets revenue p, auction terminates
if reject: bidder leaves and next bidder arrives
seller's goal: maximize expected revenue = p . Pr[at least one bidder accepts p]
